    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The building trades council extend\ned an invitation last night TO the\nMaster Builders association to meet\nthem at Central Labor hall tonight.\n\n\nThe object of the meeting is TO dis\ncuss the proposition of agreeing to\na solid wage scale for the next two\nyears.\n\n\nSecretary Potts stated today that\n1t is very doubtful whether the con-\ntractors will attend the conference\nas they have not yet signified their\nintention of accepting the Invitation."
    }
